-- Do not hide failures; preserve exit codes, stack traces, failed assertions, and actionable errors.
-
-## Safety
-- Never delete files, rewrite migrations, rotate secrets, or change production config without explicit approval.
-- Prefer small patches.
-- Run targeted tests first.
-
-## Final Response Format
-- Summary
-- Files changed
-- Tests or commands run
-- Risks or follow-up
+Read and follow `AGENTS.md`, then route through `docs/agent/INDEX.md`. Polyspace work is C-only.
+Use the canonical skill under `skills/` for every Polyspace workflow. Never auto-justify a finding,
+run generated test code without approval, enable telemetry implicitly, or overwrite unknown client
+configuration.
